<h2><a name="numbers">Numbers</a></li>
<h3>Syntax</h3>
<pre>
A.B@C
</pre>
<ul>
  <li><b>A</b>: Integral part (can be omitted if zero)</li>
  <li><b>B</b>: Decimal part (can be omitted if zero)</li>
  <li><b>C</b>: Periodic part (can be omitted if zero)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Examples</h3>
<pre>
In        Out
0.5       0.5
.5        0.5
.333333   .333333
0.@3      1/3
0.0@3     1/30
0@3       1/3
@3        1/3
.1@3      2/15
</pre>
